{"tid":2107292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個街支共","createTime":"2020-07-13T19:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T05:41:38.000Z","uid":94537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ee13002c506d674bcb068dad6247712460ed20","tid":2107292,"uid":94537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"如果唔係武肺<br />\n就唔洗同條仔半個月嚟都係一個月見4次<br />\n雜種你老母生你出嚟食屎大㗎？<br />\n我心理好唔平衡<br />\n好掛住佢好想見到佢<br />\n而加仲要翻爆，林奠你早登極樂算把啦跨境學童唔洗檢疫？<br />\n你個腦真係裝水<br />\n但佢又係衰仔，見多一兩日唔洗死嘅做咩要成日考慮咁多嘢<br />\n我只係想拍吓拖，點解咁多野限制住我㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c9dd4311b99cc1e3bebb2e36ef905a7d63c97b","tid":2107292,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:06:31.000Z","msg":"同我拍 日日見"},{"pid":"59c24e6d466a631c62b284c305633fed80da3c07","tid":2107292,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"我港台戀,冇見半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47b91e7b591699648de608c35aa748553faf08f","tid":2107292,"uid":94537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c24e6d466a631c62b284c305633fed80da3c07","tid":2107292,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"我港台戀,冇見半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:07:50.000Z","msg":"好佩服Long D可以keep到嘅情侶，覺得你哋好勁⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24214f3878bf9d2bbc9d2630fc8a23401370083","tid":2107292,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47b91e7b591699648de608c35aa748553faf08f","tid":2107292,"uid":94537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c24e6d466a631c62b284c305633fed80da3c07","tid":2107292,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite